Class SqlParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • ogdl.support.Parser
      • ogdl.template.ComplexPath
        • gstore.SqlParser

  • public class SqlParser
extends ogdl.template.ComplexPath
    SqlParser is an extension of the ComplexPath parser. It adds some productions specific for parsing SQL like queries.
